T1  - An Application of Z-Matrices to a Class of Resource Allocation Problems
AU  - Tamir, Arie
Y1  - 1976/11/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.23.3.317
